@model IEnumerable<SistemaBancario.Models.ListarSolicitudesPrestamo>
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http
@inject IHttpContextAccessor httpContextAccessor
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Lista de solicitudes de préstamos";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<head>
    <link href="~/css/dashboard.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<div class="wrapper">
    <partial name="_MenuLateral" />
    <div id="content">
        <partial name="_BarraBusqueda" />
        <section class="tables-section">
            <!-- lista de solicitudes de prestamos -->
            <div class="outer-w3-agile mt-3">
                <h4 class="tittle-w3-agileits mb-4">Lista de solicitudes de préstamo</h4>
                <table class="table table-bordered">
                    <thead class="thead-dark">
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="col">ID</th>
                            <th scope="col">Solicitante</th>
                            <th scope="col">Cedula</th>
                            <th scope="col">Monto</th>
                            <th scope="col">Tipo</th>
                            <th scope="col">Fecha de solicitud</th>
                            <th scope="col">Estado del préstamo</th>
                            <th scope="col"></th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        @foreach (var sol in Model)
                        {
                            <tr>
                                <th scope="row">@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.id_sol)</th>
                                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.solicitante)</td>
                                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.cedula)</td>
                                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.monto)</td>
                                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.tipo)</td>
                                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.fechasolicitud)</td>
                                <td>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.estado)</td>
                                <td>
                                    @if (@httpContextAccessor.HttpContext.Session.GetString("Roll") == "Cliente")
                                    {
                                        <!-- Button trigger modal -->
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" 
                                                data-toggle="modal" data-target="#exampleModal-@sol.id_sol">
                                            Detalles
                                        </button>

                                        <!-- Modal -->
                                        <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal-@sol.id_sol" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
                                                <div class="modal-content">
                                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                                        <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Detalles de la solicitud</h5>
                                                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                                                            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="modal-body">

                                                        <div class="form-row">
                                                            <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                                                                <label for="inputEmail4">Nombre del solicitante</label>
                                                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputEmail4" value="@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.solicitante)">
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                                                                <label for="inputPassword4">Cedula</label>
                                                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputPassword4" value="@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.cedula)">
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="form-row">
                                                            <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                                                                <label for="inputEmail4">Monto</label>
                                                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputEmail4" value="@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.monto)">
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                                                                <label for="inputPassword4">Tipo de préstamo</label>
                                                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputPassword4" value="@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.tipo)">
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                                                                <label for="inputPassword4">Fecha de solicitud</label>
                                                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputPassword4" value="@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.fechasolicitud)">
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="form-group">
                                                            <label for="inputAddress">Detalles de la solicitud</label>
                                                            <textarea type="text" class="form-control" id="inputAddress" rows="5">@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => sol.detalles)</textarea>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        <a class="btn btn-primary"
                                           asp-controller="Prestamos"
                                           asp-action="EditarEstadoPrestamo"
                                           asp-route-idsol="@sol.id_sol">
                                            Detalles
                                        </a>
                                    }
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        }
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <!--// lista de solicitudes de prestamos -->
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
